Intel Neural Compute Stick 2 uses OpenVINO toolkit.

Software Requirements:
OpenCV 3.4 or higher 
GNU Compiler Collection (GCC) 3.4 or higher
CMake 2.8 or higher
Python 3.5 or higher          #check version of an application :~$ <app> --version  (e.g. python3 --version)

Operating SYstem Requirements
Ubuntu 18.04.x LTS, 64-bit    #check for ubuntu updates run :~$ update-manager 
                              #check current version :~$ lsb_release -a
CentOS 7.4, 64-bit
Yocto Project v3.0, 64-bit

Installment Guide
https://docs.openvinotoolkit.org/latest/_docs_install_guides_installing_openvino_linux.html 

